Runbook
#######


Conda from: https://github.com/conda-forge/miniforge#mambaforge.

## sys setting (only once)

$> curl -LO https://github.com/conda-forge/miniforge/releases/latest/download/Mambaforge-MacOSX-arm64.sh

$> sh Mambaforge-MacOSX-arm64.sh -b -p ~/envs/conda

$> [ -f ~/envs/conda/condarc ] && mv ~/envs/conda/condarc ~/envs/conda/condarc.off || echo "good, no condarc found"

$> echo "
show_channel_urls: True
channels:
  - conda-forge
envs_dirs:
  - ~/envs
pkgs_dirs:
    - ~/envs/pkgs
" > ~/envs/conda/condarc

$> ~/envs/conda/bin/conda init

$> mamba create -n sxope --file tests/requirements.txt

## this project

$> conda activate sxope
$> jupyter notebook .

Open the notebook in alphalens/examples/tear_sheet_walk_through.ipynb
